solution:
```python
s = input()
n = len(s)
ans = float('inf')
for color in ['B', 'W']:
    count = 0
    cur = list(s)
    for i in range(n):
        if cur[i] != color:
            count += 1
            for j in range(i + 1, n):
                if cur[j] == color:
                    for k in range(i, j):
                        cur[k] = color
                    break
    ans = min(ans, count)
print(ans)

```
